   - img \"Read Today's 'Quotemeal' Devotional\"\n  - text: \"Quote by J.O.Sanders:\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e64]God does not waste suffering; if he ploughs it is because He purposes a crop.\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/quotemeal.cgi?day=20260502\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Quotemeal\" [ref=e65]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=qm&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - img\n      - text: Subscribe to Quotemeal\n  - heading \"Morning & Evening\" [ref=e66] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Morning & Evening\" [ref=e67]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/spurgeon/\n  - text: The classic twice-daily devotional from Charles H. Spurgeon.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Morning & Evening' Devotional\" [ref=e68]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spurgeon/0502-am.html\n    - img \"Read Today's 'Morning & Evening' Devotional\"\n  - text: \"Morning Thought: John 17:15\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e69] [nth=1]It is a sweet and blessed event which will occur to all believers in God's own time-the going home to be with Jesus. In a few more years the Lord's...\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spurgeon/0502-am.html\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Morning & Evening\" [ref=e70]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=me&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - img\n      - text: Subscribe to Morning & Evening\n  - heading \"Passion for Praise\" [ref=e71] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Passion for Praise\" [ref=e72]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/passionforpraise.cgi\n  - text: A daily passage of Scripture emphasizing praise to our God.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Passion for Praise' Devotional\" [ref=e73]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/passionforpraise.cgi?day=20260502\n    - img \"Read Today's 'Passion for Praise' Devotional\"\n  - text: \"'I Long for You' (Ps. 42