{"type":"message","id":"657b3d37","parentId":"ca97e626","timestamp":"2026-05-02T10:40:23.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also check OpenClaw update status and get the bills data for context.\n\nVerse: \"This is the confidence we have in approaching God: that if we ask anything according to his will, he hears us. And if we know that he hears us — whatever we ask — we know that we have what we asked of him.\" — 1 John 5:14-15\n\nNow let me get the bills and openclaw update status.\n","thinkingSignature":"cbd4e15fe5f2ef3bbf59b6980be1b0a2a128dd81288514e5cc84fce78d4e80b5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_exa7cs2o1d7f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw update status 2>&1","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_exa7cs2o1d7f_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nbills = json.load(open('/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/bills_april_2026.json'))\ntoday = datetime.now()\nupcoming = []\nfor b in bills:\n    due = datetime.strptime(b['dueDate'], '%Y-%m-%d')\n    if due <= today + timedelta(days=7):\n        status = '✅ PAID' if b.get('paid') else '⚠️ DUE'\n        upcoming.append(f'{b[\\\"name\\\"]} — {b[\\\"dueDate\\\"][5:]} — \\${b[\\\"amount\\\"]:.2f} [{status}]')\nfor u in upcoming:\n    print(u)\n\" 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4529,"output":323,"cacheRead":40128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44980,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777718413393,"responseId":"0645078dc3642bca8ec7f560614e578c"}}
