{"type":"message","id":"17cf6bc3","parentId":"d81e12bf","timestamp":"2026-05-02T10:40:37.853Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No bills file found. That's fine - I'll note in the brief that bills aren't available. Let me now send the Morning Brief sections one at a time. Let me first close the browser since I don't need it anymore.\n\nLet me now compose and send each section. I'll reference the calendar events and what I know from memory.\n\nCalendar:\n- Today: Affirm Marriott - $129.59 (9:00 AM - 9:30 AM)\n- May 5: Cinco de Mayo (US Holidays)\n- May 7: Pay KUB\n- May 8: T-Mobile - $98.30 (9:00 AM - 9:30 AM)\n- May 9: Affirm Hilton - $23.50 (9:00 AM - 9:30 AM)\n\nInactive reminders (things Bobby still needs to do):\n- Coloring Book — sell\n- Email apartments (fishkill and royal cove and ridgefield)\n- Go through all mail in Xfinity bag with Logan\n- put all bills in the family calendar\n- work on recipe app idea\n\nLet me compose each section and send them one by one.\n","thinkingSignature":"7b8b36446d66f672fcf3966240592402ad15a325d9f3cd75a0a9a79b9618af65"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d5ldrjxrvi4c_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"stop","targetId":"AA6F761826849944701760D9DFC3B8D0"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":491,"output":283,"cacheRead":44608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45382,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777718426534,"responseId":"0645079b65b138579fd7e0a62d475714"}}
