{"type":"message","id":"f0e37ce6","parentId":"d90244c4","timestamp":"2026-05-02T15:50:39.635Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check what's running on the Mac and identify the main issues:\n\n1. **WindowServer** (PID 473) — 53.9% CPU. This is unusually high. WindowServer handles all UI rendering on Mac. High CPU here usually means something is doing heavy graphics/video rendering, or there's a UI issue.\n\n2. **Telegram** (PID 46371) — 26.4% CPU. That's high for a messaging app.\n\n3. **OpenClaw gateway** (PID 68979) — 14.7% CPU, using 5.6% MEM (~473MB). This is the main OpenClaw process.\n\n\n4. **loginwindow** (PID 465) — 14.6% CPU. This shouldn't be that high either.\n\nThe system is clearly under pressure with only 49% free memory, over 283 million swapins versus 305 million swapouts, and significant memory compression happening. This suggests the system is heavily relying on swap to manage the workload.\n\nLooking at the OpenClaw side, 3 cron jobs are failing with consecutive errors - the email check has hit 3 consecutive failures while both the morning brief and email check have timed out. This could indicate either resource contention or that the isolated sessions are consuming more CPU than expected.\n\nThe main bottleneck appears to be the browser automation layer, which is likely the biggest resource drain on the system. Combined with the email agent running every hour with a very detailed payload and 3 concurrent cron jobs scheduled within the same minute window (Morning Brief Warm-Up at 5:25AM, Morning Brief at 5:30AM, and another brief at 5:30AM), the system is probably hitting memory pressure and CPU limits. I should recommend disabling or relaxing some of these cron jobs, reducing the email check frequency, and cutting back on browser usage to ease the load.\n","thinkingSignature":"d85c75449018b42cdceb8c4738be07d7fdfa6e8c7b1d3ac5ca2d6156f7bd19ad"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5k6psbd90oqn_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"mellow-lobster","timeout":15000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":228,"output":434,"cacheRead":50752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51414,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777737021355,"responseId":"0645503d6364938c7a99d418b774a063"}}
