{"type":"message","id":"05abfe44","parentId":"16af681a","timestamp":"2026-05-02T15:50:58.947Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see several things causing pressure:\n\n1. **6 active sessions** with large context windows (Rex has 57% tokens, Emmy has 42%, main has 23%)\n2. **Multiple subagents running** - Rex has 3 subagents still listed as active (d2e1943c, e25bfdb8, d8bf3289) from different times\n3. **Swap pressure** - The system has extremely high swap: 283M swapins and 305M swapouts. This is massive.\n4. **OpenClaw gateway using 14.7% CPU** and **5.6% RAM** (472MB resident) - that's significant\n\n\n5. **Telegram and WindowServer** are also consuming notable CPU alongside OpenClaw\n\nThe real issue is the combination of bloated session contexts, multiple suspended subagents still occupying memory, and heavy swap activity forcing the disk into constant use. The session cache is storing massive amounts of repeated context across these agents, leaving the system scrambling to manage memory.\n","thinkingSignature":"885c5f86f935f72f2a162041e3fc8e0b1ae7f9c3e5e9193e79816c266990dc69"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qo1kujr79p6f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw sessions list --json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\ndata = json.load(sys.stdin)\nsessions = data.get('sessions', data.get('result', []))\nprint(f'Total sessions: {len(sessions)}')\nfor s in sessions:\n    key = s.get('key', 'unknown')\n    created = s.get('createdAtMs', 0)\n    tokens = s.get('tokenCount', 0)\n    model = s.get('model', 'unknown')\n    active = s.get('activeForm', 'idle')\n    print(f'  {key[:50]:50s} | {tokens:6d} tokens | {active}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qo1kujr79p6f_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw tasks list 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":760,"output":434,"cacheRead":50944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52138,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777737039782,"responseId":"06455050bda5b45b63c85cfd8c3a9e95"}}
