{"type":"message","id":"68ad9ac8","parentId":"2528b27a","timestamp":"2026-05-02T15:53:22.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the weather cache is updated to every 1 hour. The MC Watchdog was already disabled (status: \"disabled\"). Let me verify both are in the desired state.\n\nWeather Cache: ✅ Now every 1h (was 15m)\nMC Watchdog: ✅ Already disabled\n\nLet me send Bobby a confirmation.\n","thinkingSignature":"84cc6c0c7648a47429760ab46059bf1fb133d0251b4a2bbd47a8279ba6756df5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nDone. Changes applied:\n\n**✅ MC Watchdog** — already disabled (was every 5 min). Removed from active rotation.\n\n**✅ Weather Cache Refresh** — changed from every 15 min → **every 1 hour**.\n\nHeartbeat and Emmy Email remain unchanged.\n\nThis should noticeably reduce background load. You should feel things respond faster within the next 10-15 minutes as the cron storm settles."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":521,"output":150,"cacheRead":49856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50527,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777737196579,"responseId":"064550ecd6e943f71901e80d7e6e6c9b"}}
