{"type":"message","id":"41e79aab","parentId":"65a2bcca","timestamp":"2026-05-02T15:55:19.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the mission control API and Vite dev servers are both running as LaunchAgents, but they're not responding to health checks. They might be idle/idle workers. Let me check what they actually do and whether they're necessary.\n\nAlso - I notice WindowServer at 18.4% CPU. That's elevated. And openclaw-node at 0.2% but that's just the node pairing agent.\n\nThe main culprit is still the OpenClaw gateway at 108% CPU burst (29.7% sustained). That's normal for an active agent team.\n\nLet me check if Ollama is running and if it's being used (it's not in the active workflow since we're using MiniMax).\n\n\nI should also look into whether Mission Control's services are consuming resources in the background.\n","thinkingSignature":"1039616de0a0572c56de531523e53947f0b7654443f657070b98863ce0f33d85"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ytwjjm8eole_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.bobby.missioncontrol.api.plist","timeout":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ytwjjm8eole_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.bobby.missioncontrol.vite.plist","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":534,"output":247,"cacheRead":62016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777737311306,"responseId":"0645515fb5b7f8ff6ef0aa5d11751bf4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5fa5a113","parentId":"41e79aab","timestamp":"2026-05-02T15:55:19.408Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2ytwjjm8eole_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC \"-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN\" \"http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd\">\n<plist version=\"1.0\">\n<dict>\n    <key>Label</key>\n    <string>com.bobby.missioncontrol.api</string>\n    <key>ProgramArguments</key>\n    <array>\n        <string>/bin/bash</string>\n        <string>-c</string>\n        <string>export PATH=\"/opt/homebrew/opt/node/bin:/opt/homebrew/bin:/usr/local/bin:/bin:/usr/bin\"; export XAI_API_KEY=\"xai-3i…njWd\"; cd /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control; node server/mission-control-api.cjs</string>\n    </array>\n    <key>RunAtLoad</key>\n    <true/>\n    <key>KeepAlive</key>\n    <dict>\n        <key>SuccessfulExit</key>\n        <false/>\n    </dict>\n    <key>StandardOutPath</key>\n    <string>/tmp/mc-api-launchd.log</string>\n    <key>StandardErrorPath</key>\n    <string>/tmp/mc-api-launchd.log</string>\n</dict>\n</plist>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":35,"aggregated":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC \"-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN\" \"http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd\">\n<plist version=\"1.0\">\n<dict>\n    <key>Label</key>\n    <string>com.bobby.missioncontrol.api</string>\n    <key>ProgramArguments</key>\n    <array>\n        <string>/bin/bash</string>\n        <string>-c</string>\n        <string>export PATH=\"/opt/homebrew/opt/node/bin:/opt/homebrew/bin:/usr/local/bin:/bin:/usr/bin\"; export XAI_API_KEY=\"xai-3iYJC5NPCy8m1RfTOWMaiIgBbCqjmDG4BkOuYFy4iP5Xe1fiijnMk1IirstUPbMVsC78vR7LonDFnjWd\"; cd /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control; node server/mission-control-api.cjs</string>\n    </array>\n    <key>RunAtLoad</key>\n    <true/>\n    <key>KeepAlive</key>\n    <