mpatibility │ none                                                                                          │\n│ Probes               │ skipped (use --deep)                                                                          │\n│ Events               │ none                                                                                          │\n│ Tasks                │ 1 active · 0 queued · 1 running · 95 issues · audit 19 warn · 2762 tracked                    │\n│ Heartbeat            │ 30m (main), disabled (cody), disabled (dj), disabled (emmy), disabled (finn), disabled        │\n│                      │ (reese), disabled (rex), disabled (tt), disabled (x), disabled (yoyos)                        │\n│ Sessions             │ 354 active · default gpt-5.4 (200k ctx) · 10 stores                                           │\n└──────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSecurity audit\nSkipped in fast status. Full report: openclaw security audit\nDeep probe: openclaw status --deep\n\nChannels\n┌──────────┬─────────┬────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Channel  │ Enabled │ State  │ Detail                                                                                 │\n├──────────┼─────────┼────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n└──────────┴─────────┴────────┴────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSessions\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────┬──────────┬──────────────┬────────────────────────────────┐","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777737916120}}
{"type":"message","id":"81f6c924","parentId":"21c5b983","timestamp":"2026-05-02T16:05:45.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, now I have a clear picture:\n\n1. **OpenClaw Gateway is at 101% CPU** — it's the main culprit. Running since 6:42 AM, using 11% of total RAM (923MB!)\n2. **354 active sessions** — that's enormous. Most of these are probably old/cached sessions sitting around\n3. **WindowServer at 21.3% CPU** — something is making the UI struggle\n\nKey findings:\n- OpenClaw Gateway: 101% CPU, 923MB RAM — this is the main problem\n- 354 sessions open — this is excessive and is probably what's causing the high CPU/RAM\n- MC is now stopped\n\nThe gateway process itself is the problem. It has 354 sessions and is using a ton of memory.\n\nBobby asked what else is slowing things down. The answer is:\n1. OpenClaw Gateway itself (101% CPU, 923MB RAM) with 354 sessions\n2. WindowServer (21% CPU) — UI layer struggling\n\nFor Bobby's question \"is there anything else we should look into\":\n- 354 sessions is very high — we could clean some up\n- The gateway is the bottleneck — it's doing a LOT\n\nLet me report this to Bobby clearly.\n","thinkingSignature":"d0b176fa1b5bfa800a907174f43ba04f90f7937c2211062fee8efd3f185d007b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**Mission Control is now fully stopped** ✅\n\nHere's what's left running that's consuming your Mac's resources:\n\n**The main culprit — OpenClaw Gateway:**\n- **CPU: 101%** (basically maxed out)\n- **RAM: 923MB** — very high\n- **354 active sessions** — this is the real problem\n\nEvery session OpenClaw manages takes memory + CPU overhead. Having 354 sessions open means it's juggling context from dozens of conversations across all your agents, constantly.\n\n**Other things eating resources:**\n| Process | CPU | Notes |\n|---------|-----|-------|\n| OpenClaw Gateway | 101% | Main AI system — it's the bottleneck |\n| WindowServer | 21% | UI layer struggling — too many chrome tabs? |\n| Telegram | 4% | Normal |\n| Chrome Helpers | ~1.5% | Background tabs |\n\n**What we could do:**\n\n1. **Clean up old sessions** — 354 is a lot. We could run a session cleanup (there's already a weekly cleanup cron job but it hasn't run since Apr 27). Want me to run it now?\n\n2. **Drop session cache %** — currently set to 50% which allows a lot of cached sessions. We could drop to 25% to reduce memory pressure.\n\n3. **Chrome tabs** — your WindowServer is at 21% which suggests you might have a lot of Chrome tabs open. Sometimes Chrome workers stay active in background.\n\n4. **Restart the gateway** — fresh start clears session memory. But we'd lose conversation context.\n\nThe session cleanup is probably the quickest win without disrupting anything. Want me to run it?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2241,"output":602,"cacheRead":70528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73371,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777737916123,"responseId":"064553bc6e3efb0bc134370031c829c0"}}
