{"type":"message","id":"19278d7b","parentId":"2d5df953","timestamp":"2026-05-02T16:32:35.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The TTS tool is failing with MiniMax. Let me try using the system `say` command with ffmpeg conversion, as described in TOOLS.md.","thinkingSignature":"002e611562f31d90edac8867f141dded232adef97ae5d82f53e1807aeb37f286"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xi1c9xl5v83c_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"say -v 'Samantha' \"Section 1: What is OpenClaw? OpenClaw is an autonomous AI agent that runs on your computer — think of it like having a digital employee who lives on your MacBook. It's always working, always monitoring, always ready to help. Unlike ChatGPT where you open it, ask a question, close it, and it's gone — OpenClaw stays running in the background. It checks your email, manages your files, runs automations, sends you updates, and handles all the repetitive stuff you'd otherwise have to do yourself.\n\nHere's what makes it different from other AI tools:\n\nIt's local. OpenClaw runs on your own machine, not in some distant data center. Your data stays on your computer. Your memories are stored in simple text files you can actually read and understand.\n\nIt's always on. It doesn't wait for you to ask. It monitors, reminds, checks, and coordinates throughout the day. You set up workflows once, and they run on their own.\n\nIt's built around open-source. OpenClaw started as a side project from one developer, and it grew into one of the fastest-growing open-source projects in history.\n\nIt works with tools you already use. Email, calendar, reminders, files, browsers, messaging apps — OpenClaw connects to them all.\" -o /tmp/section1_part1.aiff && ffmpeg -i /tmp/section1_part1.aiff /tmp/section1_part1.mp3 -y && cp /tmp/section1_part1.mp3 ~/.openclaw/media/section1_part1.mp3 && echo \"Part 1 done\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":940,"output":401,"cacheRead":89024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90365,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777739545571,"responseId":"06455a1945727416d1b1bf5475540cb0"}}
