{"type":"message","id":"65d2348c","parentId":"51c1aceb","timestamp":"2026-05-03T04:15:31.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to add to tomorrow's schedule: building a wiki/index-like memory system for his OpenClaw team. This is a good idea - having a shared memory bank that all agents can read/write to so they never forget anything and can always reference past conversations/decisions.\n\nThis is actually something that already partially exists in OpenClaw (memory files, MEMORY.md, etc.) but Bobby wants to make it more robust and systematic. A \"wiki-like index\" for all his agents.\n\nI'll add it to the plan - after the guide and recipe rip work, or maybe as a standalone task. Let me add it to the schedule.\n","thinkingSignature":"e679e57792ac410a18dd3a895e036554c53eb2ef3b159bbedec62cb71bae045e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nAdding it to tomorrow's schedule. It would go after the OpenClaw Guide + Recipe Rip work, or we could swap things around — depends on energy. Here's what it'll look like:\n\n---\n\n**YOUR DAY (Sat May 3)**\n\n⏰ 6:30 AM — Wake up, coffee\n\n🚗 8-11 AM — DoorDash shift\n\n🛒 11 AM — Kroger/Publix (oranges, 100% apple juice, coffee)\n\n🍳 12 PM — Eggs + toast + rice + Logan\n\n💰 1 PM — Finn: May bills review + finance update\n\n📝 2-4 PM — OpenClaw Guide (finish Sections 2-4)\n\n🧑‍💻 4-5 PM — Recipe Rip (pricing + landing page)\n\n🧠 5-6 PM — **Build the Memory Wiki** — index system so every agent remembers everything, forever\n\n---\n\n**What I need from you to prep for tomorrow:**\n\nWhen you talk to Finn tonight or tomorrow, mention what May bills are coming and any changes to your cash flow. And when we build the memory wiki, I'll need you to walk me through:\n\n- What you want indexed (every conversation? only decisions? agent outputs?)\n- How you want it organized (by topic? by date? by project?)\n- What you want agents to know before they talk to you\n\nWe'll figure that out together tomorrow. Get some rest — I'll be ready. 🤖🦞"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":118734,"output":439,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119365,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777781700653,"responseId":"0645fec5bde0b6f8e32371057bc0bc7a"}}
