{"type":"message","id":"3a247ba5","parentId":"b3be67bf","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:15:52.027Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I created the folder structure. Now let me build out the wiki files with what I know about Bobby. Let me work on this in the background and keep building throughout the night.\n\nLet me spawn a subagent to work on this throughout the night while I stay responsive to Bobby.\n\nActually, I should spawn a subagent to work on this. But wait - I should also write to memory so Bobby can check in and see progress. Let me spawn a background task that works on this and updates a progress file.\n","thinkingSignature":"796aefb46bb855face03215524f296d621f6f6878ac4c39043ed32e48b9537c8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ew8qqgw5xbuh_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"session","runtime":"subagent","task":"Build Bobby's Memory Wiki system overnight. Work quietly, don't send messages, just build files.\n\nBASE PATH: /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/\n\nFOLDER STRUCTURE (already created):\n- people/ → Logan (husband), family, friends, contacts\n- projects/ → OpenClaw Guide, Recipe Rip, @profittopanic, @whythoughtv, content channels\n- preferences/ → Bobby's preferences, habits, schedule patterns\n- finances/ → bills, cash flow, income sources (DoorDash, content)\n- content/ → YouTube, TikTok, X/Twitter content ideas and notes\n- routines/ → daily schedules, morning routine, evening routine\n- systems/ → how OpenClaw is set up, skills, cron jobs\n- connections/ → links between files (the \"orb\" concept)\n\nPHASE 1 - CORE FILES (before 3 AM):\nCreate these files with MAXIMUM detail:\n\n1. /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/people/logan.md\n2. /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/people/bobby.md (full profile)\n3. /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/projects/openclaw-guide.md\n4. /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/projects/recipe-rip.md\n5. /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/finances/may-2026-bills.md\n6. /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/preferences/daily-schedule.md\n7. /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/systems/openclaw-setup.md\n8. /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/connections/index.md (master link map)\n\nPHASE 2 - CROSS-LINKS (3 AM - 6 AM):\nBuild the connection system. Each file should reference related files.\nExample: openclaw-guide.md should link to systems/openclaw-setup.md, content/youtube-channels.md, etc.\n\nPHASE 3 - THE ORB (5 AM - 6 AM):\nCreate a visual index at connections/orb.md that shows how everything connects.\n\nEVERY FILE SHOULD:\n- Be written in Bobby's voice (3rd person \"Bobby\" not \"you\")\n- Include date stamps\n- Link to related files using [[filename]] style\n- Be as detailed as possible\n- Include everything known about that topic\n\nWrite progress to: /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/PROGRESS.md\n\nStart NOW. Work through the night. Be thorough and detailed. When done around 6 AM, write \"DONE\" to PROGRESS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":434,"output":745,"cacheRead":119744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120923,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777785335960,"responseId":"06460cf8e7e7641f29c36f119563f2a4"}}
