{"type":"message","id":"c1d39168","parentId":"8e151c35","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:24:45.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants the memory wiki to be a living system where everything he tells any agent gets stored there. I need to:\n\n1. Tell the other agents (Emmy, Finn, Rex, etc.) to log everything Bobby tells them to the memory wiki\n2. Set up a system so that when Bobby tells any agent something, they file it in the wiki\n3. This needs to be an ongoing operational rule\n\nI should tell Bobby I'll set this up, and also possibly update the agents' configurations to always log to the wiki. This might require updating each agent's system prompt/SOUL.md or setting up a shared protocol.\n\nLet me be brief and actionable.\n","thinkingSignature":"cfb5a42138aa5cbc51050bddcd3eaab73c7dc1e5f7ab8ff536f9782495d9d60b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nGot it. I'll make sure every agent on your team logs everything you tell them to the wiki. Here's what I'm going to do:\n\n**Right now:**\n- Update each agent's instructions so they know to file everything Bobby says into the memory wiki\n- Set up a shared protocol — when you tell Emmy something, she drops it in `finances/` or `preferences/`. When Finn tells you something, same thing.\n\n**Ongoing:**\n- Every conversation you have with any agent → logged, linked, timestamped\n- Nothing falls through the cracks anymore\n\nI'll update all the agents now and make sure they all know the system. Sleep — I'll have it running by morning. 🤖🦞"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":122862,"output":280,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123270,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777785870711,"responseId":"06460f0f2d9804e57e5ded471709e91d"}}
