{"type":"message","id":"fc020e1e","parentId":"425a2c51","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:42:05.230Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby has given me very clear answers:\n\n1. Full transcripts for everything + summaries + hybrid on important topics\n2. Both - daily logs per agent AND a connected wiki\n3. Yes - agents can read each other's logs\n4. Searchable by date, topic, project, person, keyword — everything\n5. Changes allowed but only with Bobby's approval\n\nThis is a comprehensive, well-thought-out system. Let me confirm I understand and start building it right. This is going to be a solid memory system for Bobby's whole team.\n","thinkingSignature":"767230a801137efcda14791dc2ce11adff93494b95a6a8260dae1e8a79c4c90f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nYes Bobby — I understand perfectly. Here's what I'm building:\n\n**Daily Logs (per agent, per day):**\n- Every word you say to Emmy → Emmy-May-03.md (full transcript)\n- Every word you say to Finn → Finn-May-03.md\n- Same for every agent\n- Summary attached to each conversation\n\n**Connected Wiki (cross-linked):**\n- Topic files that pull from all agents\n- money.md — Finn's notes + Emmy's notes + Dean's notes, all linked\n- guide.md — YoYo, Cody, Dean all add to it\n- Nothing contradictory, everything connected\n\n**Searchable by everything:**\n- Date, topic, project, person, keyword — all of it\n\n**Agents can correct things:**\n- But only after they ask you → you approve → it gets updated\n- Wrong info gets flagged, not silently changed\n\n**Your whole team reads each other:**\n- Emmy knows what Finn told you\n- Finn knows what Rex found\n- Everyone stays in sync\n\nI'll have this running by morning. Get some rest — your team is about to have the best memory system you've ever had. 🤖🦞"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":123444,"output":349,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123921,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777786903271,"responseId":"0646131807812e0df356eefdc872c963"}}
