{"type":"message","id":"a9849427","parentId":"90be9334","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:44:01.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is clarifying - the memory wiki shouldn't be siloed by agent. Each agent shouldn't be restricted to their own category. Instead, everything goes into a unified system where any agent can add to any topic, and all agents can read everything. The wiki is shared, not siloed by agent.\n\nSo the structure is more like:\n- One big connected wiki\n- Agents all contribute to it freely\n- Daily logs exist as raw records but everything also gets organized into topic files\n- All agents can read all files\n- Agents can add to any file, not just their \"assigned\" category\n\nThe daily logs are more like the raw source of truth (every conversation verbatim), and then the wiki files are the organized distillation that all agents maintain together.\n\nLet me clarify this understanding and confirm.\n","thinkingSignature":"93f0a7a74705af94fb17ef07139429b59a6b5df25e628b24cdb2694641ebcd50"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nRight — one shared brain, not separate folders per agent. The master claw memory system is:\n\n**One unified wiki** — any agent can add to any file\n**Daily raw logs** — record everything verbatim, timestamped, who was there\n**Wiki organizes it** — facts, decisions, preferences all connected across topics\n**All agents read everything** — full team knowledge, not siloed\n\nSo if you tell Emmy about a bill and Finn about the same bill — they both write to `finances/may-2026-bills.md`, cross-linked, and it all connects to `preferences/bobby-schedule.md` and everything else.\n\nThe daily log is just the raw record. The wiki is the organized brain that every agent shares.\n\nI'm building this now. Sleep — your whole team wakes up knowing everything. 🤖🦞"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":123723,"output":334,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124185,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777787027557,"responseId":"064613940e81d13d9074f1f7fddf7640"}}
