{"type":"message","id":"51ed965e","parentId":"b6446dc9","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:46:04.867Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll spawn a subagent to build this properly overnight, with all the details from our conversation.","thinkingSignature":"6fd9017ccba2e13fd985b51a497eb8c27d1658b8bcea2c13ee72d25ff63ef9a9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ae07olfgjt94_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"Build Bobby's Master Claw Memory System. Work through the night silently. Build at /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/\n\nFOLDER STRUCTURE:\n- daily-logs/ — raw verbatim logs per agent per day (agent name + date)\n- wiki/ — organized knowledge organized by topic\n- archive/ — old logs, completed work\n- pending/ — things waiting for Bobby's approval to change\n- search-index/ — keywords and cross-references for fast lookup\n\nRULES FOR THE SYSTEM:\n1. ALL agents can read and write to ALL folders — no agent siloing\n2. daily-logs/ contains verbatim transcripts from every conversation, timestamped\n3. wiki/ contains organized knowledge, cross-linked with [[links]]\n4. Agents flag info for change — it goes to pending/ until Bobby approves\n5. Everything searchable by date, topic, keyword, person, project\n6. Daily logs written in 3rd person \"Bobby\" not \"you\"\n7. Every file links to related files\n\nPHASE 1 — CORE STRUCTURE:\nCreate these foundation files NOW:\n\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/SYSTEM.md — explains the whole system, rules, how to use\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/ARCHITECTURE.md — folder structure, what goes where\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/template.md — template for daily logs\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/template.md — template for wiki files\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/master-index.md — the main organized brain\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/search-index/keywords.md — searchable keyword index\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/pending/INDEX.md — things waiting for Bobby approval\n\nPHASE 2 — INITIAL CONTENT:\nPopulate the wiki with what you already know about Bobby:\n\nwiki/bobby.md — full profile (Lives Knoxville TN 37922, husband Logan, MacBook Air 8GB, goals to replace income with AI team, has @profittopanic + @whythoughtv YouTube channels, building OpenClaw Guide to sell, Recipe Rip app, wants to DoorDash for income)\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/logan.md — husband details\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/openclaw-guide.md — guide project\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/recipe-rip.md — Recipe Rip project\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/goals.md — short + long term goals\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/finances.md — money situation, bills, income\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/setup.md — OpenClaw setup details\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/preferences.md — Bobby's preferences and habits\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/projects.md — all active projects\n\ndaily-logs/2026-05-02.md — today's raw log: everything Bobby discussed today (memory wiki, schedule for tomorrow, DoorDash, breakfast plan, Finn bills review, all of it)\n\nPHASE 3 — SEARCH INDEX:\nBuild a keyword index that maps topics to files. Every important word or topic should point to where it lives in the wiki.\n\nPHASE 4 — CROSS LINK EVERYTHING:\nEvery file in wiki/ should link to at least 3 other files. Build connections/orb.md showing how the whole wiki is connected.\n\nPHASE 5 — AGENT PROTOCOLS:\nCreate a file that tells every agent how to use this system:\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/AGENT-PROTOCOL.md\n\nWrite progress to PROGRESS.md. When fully done, write \"DONE — Master Claw Memory System Built\" to PROGRESS.md\n\nWork through the night. Be thorough. This is Bobby's brain.","timeoutSeconds":21600}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":89,"output":985,"cacheRead":124032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125106,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777787153788,"responseId":"064614110b8926409510a6d82b547a4d"}}
